35#include <drm/drmP.h>
36#include <drm/drm_fb_helper.h>
37
38struct radeonfb_attach_args {

40 struct drm_fb_helper_surface_size rfa_fb_sizes;

43};

45#endif /* _RADEON_RADEONDRMKMS_H_ */
